name: Eugenia jambos

details: EUGENIA produces a state of intoxication like alcohol. Everything appears beautiful and larger; excitement soon changing to depression. Acne, simple and indurated. The pimples are painful for some distance around. Acne rosacea. NAUSEA. BETTER SMOKING. COMEDONES.
